        <updateDate>2019-09-05T15:56:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Veterans Hearing Benefits Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a presumption of service-connection for veterans with permanent hearing loss, tinnitus, or both, who served on active duty in combat or in a military occupational specialty in which they were exposed to a high level of acoustic trauma. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
